{"tid":2295873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光:未有充份數據將新冠肺炎列入職業病","createTime":"2020-11-22T05:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T11:58:33.000Z","uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5cead157020b8974fb0767261ae2d5d59f01489","tid":2295873,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20200419130722&amp;page=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FSearchText%3D%26NewsId%3D20200419130722%26page%3D0&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=1ff75fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20200419130722&amp;page=0</a><br />\n<br />\n羅致光:未有充份數據將新冠肺炎列入職業病<br />\n<br />\n19/4/2020 13:07<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;對於有意見要求將新型冠狀病毒列入職業病, 勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示, 根據國際勞工組織的定義, 職業病是指疾病與工作存在因果關係, 但當疾病在社區廣泛傳播時, 不可以假設受感染的醫護人員是在工作中感染, 醫護人員感染病毒的風險因地方而異, 如果採取足夠及有效的措施, 就能控制工作時受感染的風險.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"red\">&nbsp;羅致光在網誌表示, 如果僱員在工作期間因工受傷或死亡, 僱員仍可根據僱員補償條例向僱主追討補償, 衞生署會追踪接觸者報告, 提供證據, 協助僱員追討</span>.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/UB5WOKE2H5E55N2S4VVXE6HUHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FUB5WOKE2H5E55N2S4VVXE6HUHQ%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=b8f1a9b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FUB5WOKE2H5E55N2S4VVXE6HUHQ%2F&h=77ca82f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/UB5WOKE2H5E55N2S4VVXE6HUHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n因為港府堅拒全面封關、抗疫措施以政治考慮為先，武漢肺炎疫情持續10個月未息，連累5,311人染疫。亦因政府寧死不把武肺納為職業病，打工仔患病也難以爭取任何賠償。食物及衞生局回覆醫學界立法會議員陳沛然提問時披露，<span class=\"red\">勞工處接獲217宗懷疑因工染疫的僱員補償個案，只有1宗成功申領補償，比率僅0.46%。...</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個垃圾政府d政策點解可以自相矛盾到咁嘅地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有正路唔揀，尊登揀條中招派5000歪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ac9761b88ec6dc0044837e647e73f33ec38187","tid":2295873,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"市民:有充份證據將弱智列入政治委任官員常見職業病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487c30e8d641bdd3b5366224d91d9565b3795742","tid":2295873,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4ac9761b88ec6dc0044837e647e73f33ec38187","tid":2295873,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"市民:有充份證據將弱智列入政治委任官員常見職業病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f798b0388ed2146a2212bfb6544b92884c03096","tid":2295873,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"$1000蚊一樽肺炎細菌唾液，有冇人有興趣？響應政府鼓勵市民確診肺炎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2295857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2295857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"039bb4518572251f081869810a135f503baf3940","tid":2295873,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工要求封關就鬥氣<br />\n個個香港人防疫你又免檢<br />\n奶野就市民問題你死你事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩到香港大爆發你估你走唔走唔得甩"},{"pid":"7c02dab77beb585641f116bd4e45f81a0ffbccda","tid":2295873,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}